DESCRIPTION
-----------

A fork based applcation that could keep track of processes running different functions paralelly and pass messages between them.

INSTALLATION AND RUNNING
------------------------
In order to run the current version of the extended scheduler, 

1. Run 'make install'. 
2. ./sched_ext_mngr

CHANGELOG
---------

04/04/2011 v1.0 - Basic data structure implemented
12/04/2011 v1.1 - A runnable prototype running two (or more) different functions paralelly.
